main: ^Ingrid: Astrid, Astrid, oh, my poor little girl, please tell me you aren’t hurt.
^Astrid: I’m fine mommy, Brokkr saved me!
^Ingrid: That he did. Thank you so much Brokkr! Are you alright dear?
^Ingrid: Come on Astrid, time to get home. Thank you again Brokkr. I’ll come over with some goods for you and your father one day. Blessed be you!
